QuestData.Title: Stronger Than Reeds
QuestData.Description: Gather me reeds from the nearby pools.$B$BDo not question why. Do, and then observe the results.
QuestData.CompletionText: Telling you of my strength means nothing. I must show you.
QuestData.RewardText: Good.$B$BNo number of reeds have ever withstood my might.$B$BStep back, and let me dispel your doubts.
